{"meta":{"title":"Morôni 3","canonicalUrl":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/3?lang=por","contentType":"text/html","audio":[{"mediaUrl":"https://media2.ldscdn.org/assets/scriptures/the-book-of-mormon-another-testament-of-jesus-christ//2013-06-254-moroni-03-64k-por.mp3","voice":{"name":"audio"}}],"pageAttributes":{"data-asset-id":"41afbca06f250a29ded9eb7cd72d2147a5dfc662","data-aid":"124207990","data-aid-version":"2","data-content-type":"chapter","data-uri":"/scriptures/bofm/moro/3","itemscope":"","itemtype":"http://schema.org/Article","lang":"por","data-orig-id":"d8eea313723aec5fb2100222f4e6778642ead1e4","xmlns:xsi":"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance"}},"content":{"head":{"page-meta-social":{"pageMeta":{"title":"Morôni 3","description":"Os élderes ordenam sacerdotes e mestres pela imposição de mãos. Aproximadamente 401–421 d.C."},"pageSocial":{"title":"Morôni 3","description":"Os élderes ordenam sacerdotes e mestres pela imposição de mãos. Aproximadamente 401–421 d.C."}},"links":[{"type":"array","rel":"stylesheet","orig-type":"text/css","href":"css/style_classic-scripture.css"}],"scripts":[]},"body":"<header>\n<p class=\"title-number\" data-aid=\"124208266\" id=\"title_number1\">Capítulo 3</p>\n<p class=\"study-summary\" data-aid=\"124208269\" id=\"study_summary1\">Os élderes ordenam sacerdotes e mestres pela imposição de mãos. Aproximadamente 401–421 d.C.</p>\n</header>\n<div class=\"body-block\">\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"124208272\" id=\"p1\"><span class=\"verse-number\">1 </span>Maneira pela qual os discípulos, que eram chamados de <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note1a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>élderes</a> da igreja, <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note1b\"><sup class=\"marker\">b</sup>ordenavam</a> sacerdotes e mestres —</p>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"124208276\" id=\"p2\"><span class=\"verse-number\">2 </span>Depois de haverem orado ao Pai, em nome de Cristo, impunham-lhes as mãos e diziam:</p>\n<span class=\"page-break\" data-page=\"606\"></span>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"124208281\" id=\"p3\"><span class=\"verse-number\">3 </span>Em nome de Jesus Cristo eu te ordeno sacerdote (ou, se fosse mestre, eu te ordeno mestre), a fim de pregares o arrependimento e a <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note3a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>remissão</a> dos pecados por intermédio de Jesus Cristo, pela perseverança na fé em seu nome até o fim. Amém.</p>\n<p class=\"verse\" data-aid=\"124208286\" id=\"p4\"><span class=\"verse-number\">4 </span>E deste modo <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note4a\"><sup class=\"marker\">a</sup>ordenavam</a> sacerdotes e mestres, de acordo com os <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note4b\"><sup class=\"marker\">b</sup>dons</a> e chamados de Deus aos homens; e ordenavam-nos pelo <a class=\"study-note-ref\" href=\"#note4c\"><sup class=\"marker\">c</sup>poder</a> do Espírito Santo que neles estava.</p>\n</div>\n<footer class=\"study-notes\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"chapter\">\n<li data-marker=\"3\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"verse\">\n<li data-marker=\"1\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note1a\" data-full-marker=\"1a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124208292\" id=\"note1a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/alma/6.1?lang=por#p1\">Al. 6:1</a>. <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/elder?lang=por\"><small>GEE</small> Élder (Ancião)</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"b\" id=\"note1b\" data-full-marker=\"1b\">\n<p data-aid=\"124208297\" id=\"note1b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/ordain-ordination?lang=por\"><small>GEE</small> Ordenação, Ordenar</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"3\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note3a\" data-full-marker=\"3a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124208303\" id=\"note3a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/remission-of-sins?lang=por\"><small>GEE</small> Remissão de Pecados</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"4\">\n<ul class=\"marker\" data-type=\"marker\">\n<li data-marker=\"a\" id=\"note4a\" data-full-marker=\"4a\">\n<p data-aid=\"124208310\" id=\"note4a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/18.32?lang=por#p32\">D&amp;C 18:32</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/20.60?lang=por#p60\">20:60</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"b\" id=\"note4b\" data-full-marker=\"4b\">\n<p data-aid=\"124208315\" id=\"note4b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/gift?lang=por\"><small>GEE</small> Dom</a>.</p>\n</li>\n<li data-marker=\"c\" id=\"note4c\" data-full-marker=\"4c\">\n<p data-aid=\"124208320\" id=\"note4c_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/13.37?lang=por#p37\">1 Né. 13:37</a>; <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/moro/6.9?lang=por#p9\">Morô. 6:9</a>.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</footer>","footnotes":{"note1a":{"id":"note1a","marker":"1a","pid":"124208272","context":"élderes","text":"<p data-aid=\"124208292\" id=\"note1a_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/bofm/alma/6.1?lang=por#p1\">Al. 6:1</a>. <a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/elder?lang=por\"><small>GEE</small> Élder (Ancião)</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/bofm/alma/6.1?lang=por#p1","text":"Al. 6:1"},{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/gs/elder?lang=por","text":"GEE Élder (Ancião)"}]},"note1b":{"id":"note1b","marker":"1b","pid":"124208272","context":"ordenavam","text":"<p data-aid=\"124208297\" id=\"note1b_p1\"><a class=\"scripture-ref\" href=\"/study/scriptures/gs/ordain-ordination?lang=por\"><small>GEE</small> Ordenação, Ordenar</a>.</p>","referenceUris":[{"type":"scripture-ref","href":"/study/scriptures/gs/ordain-ordination?lang=por","text":"GEE Ordenação, Ordenar"}]},"note3a":{"id":"note3a","marker":"3a","pid":